articles.title: French Open: ‘I don’t support war,’ Belarusian Sabalenka says - Al Jazeera English
articles.description: Sabalenka says she does not support President Alexander Lukashenko ‘right now’ after win over Ukraine’s Elina Svitolina.
articles.content: World tennis number two Belarusian Aryna Sabalenka has said she does not support the war in Ukraine and the stance of her countrys president on it, as she resumed her media duties at the French Open.… [+4348 chars]
